        "content": "## 📝 WORKFLOW OVERVIEW\n\nThis n8n workflow provides AI-powered research assistance:\n\n🌐 **Internet Search** (SerpAPI)\n- Real-time web search capabilities via Google\n\n📚 **Document Search** (Supabase RAG)\n- Search through your private documents\n- Requires Supabase project setup",
        "height": 464,
        "width": 569,
        "color": 5
