    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🌐 INTERNET SEARCH\n\n**API:** SerpAPI (Google)\n**Purpose:** Real-time internet search\n\n**Setup Required:**\n1. Configure SerpAPI credentials in n8n\n\n**What it does:**\n- Searches Google for live content\n- Returns current information\n- Perfect for news, trends, product info",
        "height": 419,
        "width": 310
      },
      "id": "c454c4fe-1254-48f2-9616-d66e301a7962",
      "name": "Sticky Note1",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
