        640
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📚 RAG SETUP (Optional)\n\nThis workflow is ready for RAG! \n\n**To enable:**\n1. Create a Supabase project\n2. Add your Supabase credentials to the 'Supabase Vector Store Node' below\n3. Run the ingestion script (from `supabase-rag` folder) to upload docs\n\nNow your agent can search your private data!",
        "height": 639,
        "width": 318
      },
      "id": "3c69bddb-c4e4-4f95-b66b-c2909cab9a2e",
